title: Return of Starfleet One
info:
I made this tune originally for the Heavenly Compo 2 in 1999.
The result was place #22.

Also an slightly edited version of this track has been used for the dbf Phenoma Challenge entry:[url=http://www.dbfinteractive.com/forum/index.php?topic=5418.0"]Here comes the sun[/url]

The intro was voted 1st place.
